Sequence Information.Peptide Name: CFPS_AMP_13 (cell-free protein synthesis-AMP 13, Lys-rich, AI predicted AMPs, UCLL1)
Sequence Information.Source: AI predicted, machine learning prediction of known protein sequences

Literature.Author: Pandi A, Adam D, Zare A, Trinh VT, Schaefer SL, Burt M, Klabunde B, Bobkova E, Kushwaha M, Foroughijabbari Y, Braun P, Spahn C, Preußer C, Pogge von Strandmann E, Bode HB, von Buttlar H, Bertrams W, Jung AL, Abendroth F, Schmeck B, Hummer G, Vázquez O, Erb TJ. 2023

Sequence Information.Comments: Sequence analysis: APD analysis reveals that this sequence is most similar (39.22%) toBF-CATH. K: 31%; F: 10%.Activity: active against E. coli (MIC 25 uM), B. subtilis (MIC 1.6 uM), A. baumannii clinical strain (MIC 3.1 uM), Enterobacter spp. (MIC >25 uM), K. pneumoniae DSM 30104 (MIC 6.3 uM), P. aeruginosa DSM 1117 (MIC 12.5 uM), S. aureus DSM 11729 MRSA (MIC 12.5 uM), E. faecium (MIC 1.6 uM), Y. pestis EV76 (MIC 25 uM), B. anthracis Sterne (MIC 25 uM), and S. pneumoniae D39 (MIC 12.5 uM).Toxicity: Human RBC: HC50>250 uM, not hemo.lytic.Resistance development:no:bacteria:E. coli: E. coli did not develop resistance to the peptide after 21 passages.
